ate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311063/dji-flip-folding-drone-fcc-leak</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-12-02T12:43:29-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-02T12:43:29-05:00</updated><title> Google 地图现在显示位智事件报告</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google 地图徽标的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/2swaeglAdxXw_Efm1LHyFeFr1Co=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73761021/STK270_GOOGLE_MAPS_D.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ZL86pr&quot;>;Google 地图现在开始在您导航时显示 Waze 事件报告，并包括通过确认道路状况来做出贡献的功能应用程序通过提示。 Google &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/31/24209969/google-maps-destination-guidance-waze-camera-events&quot;>;于 7 月宣布&lt;/a>;这两款应用将交叉传播更多数据，将更多 Waze 来源的道路封闭、施工、超速摄像头和警察存在信息传送到 Google 地图中。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;6rXw4y&quot;>;据 &lt;a href=&quot;https://9to5google.com/2024/11/30/google-maps-waze-reports/&quot;>;&lt;em>;9to5Google&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 报道和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.androidauthority.com/google-maps-waze-reports-3504512/&quot;>;&lt;em>;Android Authority&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;，在假期周末，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reddit.com/r/GoogleMaps/comments/1h38vj1/google_maps_now_sharing_waze_user_reports/?rdt=57396&quot;>;一位 Reddit 用户&lt;/a>;分享了一张提示屏幕截图，显示“警方提前报告”，基于位智司机的报告。与地图中的其他事件通知一样，用户可以更新报告以记录是否仍然看到相同的内容。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：Reddit 用户 &lt;a class= “ql-link”href =“https://www.reddit.com/r/GoogleMaps/comments/1h38vj1/google_maps_now_sharing_waze_user_reports/?rdt=57396” target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Truckin_18&lt;/a>;&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;非常 Waze-y...&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311129/google-map-waze-integration-incident-reporting-rollout&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311129/google-map-waze-integration-incident-reporting-rollout" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311129/google-map-waze-integration-incident-reporting-rollout</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry></feed>